//- carlin departure (logged in README): mixin hoisted out of the `- let`
//- body — definitions are top-level only (Q10); the omitted call argument
//- is an explicit nil — arity is exact (spec §3.13)
mixin item [icon]
  li
    if (:href attributes)
      a&attributes attributes
        img.icon{:src icon}
        block
    else
      span&attributes attributes
        img.icon{:src icon}
        block

- (let [tag "p" foo "bar"])
  #{tag} value
  #{tag}{:foo "bar"} value
  #{(if foo "a" "li")}{:something true} here

  ul
    +(item "contact")
      | Contact
    +(item nil){:href "/contact"}
      | Contact
